	"We use the Open Collective platform to collect donations.": "",
	"Also see the complete lists of <a href='https://github.com/luanti-org/luanti/graphs/contributors'>Luanti</a> and <a href='https://github.com/luanti-org/minetest_game/graphs/contributors'>Minetest Game</a> contributors.": "",
	"The UNEJ project (*Urbanités Numériques En Jeux*) is a 4 years project where teachers and students discover about urban planning while building concrete proposals for their neighborhood's development with the help of professionals from the sector. It is done in connection with the urban transformations carried out for the 2024 Olympics.": "",
	"For good first tasks, look out for the \"good first issue\" label on the <a href='https://github.com/luanti-org/luanti/issues?q=is%3Aissue+is%3Aopen+sort%3Aupdated-desc+label%3A%22good+first+issue%22'>engine</a> or <a href='https://github.com/luanti-org/luanti-org.github.io/issues?q=is%3Aissue+is%3Aopen+sort%3Aupdated-desc+label%3A%22good+first+issue%22'>website</a> repositories.": "",
